name: How And Why We Do Stuff
body:
# Welcome to Western Cape Labs

This is where we describe how we get stuff done and why we do the things we do.

If something is missing, you find mistakes, or you want to contribute with your experiences and additional information [create an issue](https://github.com/westerncapelabs/westerncapelabs.github.io/issues).
